data.description: This 3-bedroom, 2-bath manufactured home is a wonderful property with a range of attractive features. The park-like setting on almost 2 acres, detached oversized garage, and fenced backyard contribute to the overall appeal. The split plan with a large owner's suite featuring a walk-in closet adds a comfortable touch, with dual vanities and a soaking tub in the owner's bath. The upgraded door hardware, wainscoting, and textured walls showcase attention to detail and enhance the aesthetic of the home. The kitchen island with an outlet adds functionality and convenience. The washer and dryer will remain with the home. The laundry room's sink and 220v outlet are convenient additions. The inclusion of two sheds with the property provides additional storage space. There is a 30-amp RV connection in the garage. The combination of city water and septic is practical. Given the convenient location near shopping, Augusta, and Aiken, this property is a well-rounded and desirable option for your living enjoyment.  Call today to schedule your showing!
